text: Jensen Ross Ackles (born March 1, 1978) is an American television actor. He is best known for his role as Dean Winchester in the television series Supernatural (2005â€“present). He has also appeared in other television shows such as Days of Our Lives, Dark Angel and Smallville. Ackles was born in Dallas, Texas. He is the son of Alan Ackles, also an actor. He has been married to Danneel Ackles since 2010.
